Introduction

Oh Taehwan is a South Korean trainee.

On August 14, 2023, he was revealed as a contestant on MBC's survival show Fan Pick. He was sadly eliminated of the show and wasn't able to debut in the final group.

On September 26, 2024, he was revealed as a contestant on JTBC's survival show PROJECT7 starting in October 2024.
